00:21:08.400 --> 00:21:09.868 line:95%,end
LESLIE: Because it was
uncomfortable for Payton and I.

00:21:10.102 --> 00:21:12.738 line:95%,end
We came in to fill in
for you and your child.

00:21:12.804 --> 00:21:14.706 line:95%,end
KELLY: And did I tell
Payton and you to leave?

00:21:14.906 --> 00:21:16.375 line:95%,end
LESLIE: But it still
makes her uncomfortable

00:21:16.441 --> 00:21:18.010 line:95%,end
because she's
there to take Brooke's spot.

00:21:18.110 --> 00:21:19.111 line:95%,end
I'm a part of the team.

00:21:19.211 --> 00:21:20.612 line:95%,end
How many times do you
think it takes for you

00:21:20.679 --> 00:21:21.913 line:95%,end
