Well, I'm not a wacko.

00:21:54.513 --> 00:21:56.882 line:95%,end
JEFF: All right.
- Your eyes say something different.

00:21:56.948 --> 00:21:57.949 line:95%,end
OK.
- Good.

00:21:58.050 --> 00:21:59.051 line:95%,end
