The only thing we asked
is that she had the courtesy

00:22:37.823 --> 00:22:39.157 line:95%,end
to give us a call--
JEFF: Right.

00:22:39.224 --> 00:22:41.093 line:95%,end
--to notify us. That was the only thing.
