herself up on Instagram.

00:23:29.708 --> 00:23:31.176 line:95%,end
HOLLY: Oh, that's really recent.

00:23:31.877 --> 00:23:33.845 line:5%,start
CHRISTI: Abby's all about making money.

00:23:33.912 --> 00:23:36.381 line:95%,end
If some competition dangles
cash in front of her

00:23:36.448 --> 00:23:38.717 line:95%,end
to go judge a competition,
she'll be there.

00:23:38.784 --> 00:23:40.952 line:95%,end
- Maybe she's at a meet and greet.
