00:23:41.286 --> 00:23:44.423 line:95%,end
She was out of competition
for three hours, so she is very--

00:23:44.489 --> 00:23:46.391 line:95%,end
JILL: But she didn't to tell us that.

00:23:46.458 --> 00:23:48.727 line:95%,end
JEFF: All right. So Christi,
now, we understand that you all

00:23:48.794 --> 00:23:50.695 line:95%,end
